snippet.title: Amber Heard's Future As Mera In Question For Aquaman 2 Johnny Depp VS Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Amber Heard's Future As Mera In Question For Aquaman 2 Johnny Depp VS Amber Heard


per boundingintocomics - Warner Bros. is not firing Amber Heard despite her bad publicity from the ongoing defamation suit against her. But they may have figured their way around things. Grace Randolph tweeted steps might be taken to reduce Heard’s part in Aquaman 2 if need be. The same holds true for Johnny Depp.
